Hi Markus,

This error happens when the pingcastle.exe cannot have its digital signature verified by the operating system. Can you tell if you built this yourself as this is a common way this can happen. If not, then check the digital signature of the file and see how it looks as maybe it is not trusting one of our certificates?
 
Should look something like this but yours may say it cannot be verified or something?
